This is an input program written in Scala for Timecard project using camera
(typically webcam).

Supported platform: Linux (tested on Ubuntu 10.4 64 bit)

== COMPILE

Install v4l4j:
* Goto http://code.google.com/p/v4l4j/downloads/list
* Download and install, for example if your Linux is 64 bit:
libvideo0_xxx_amd64.deb
libv4l4j-java_xxx_amd64.deb
libv4l4j-bin_xxx_all.deb (optional)

Compile using SBT:
sbt update
sbt compile
